rules:
1. Only translate the Chinese part, do not translate the English specific words.
2. For the system route part, do not translate, e.g. D:\工作\任务\bug处理\SWY-79001\1.pdf.
3. Do not translate every placeholder and keep them the same like %%s.
4. For the URL, please only translate the Chinese part, do not translate the English specific words, e.g. https://www.baidu.com.
5. For the format [# #], do not translate the English specific words, e.g. [# SWY-79001#], [#taskname#].
6. For the format <%= %%s %%>, do not translate the English specific words, e.g. <%=propName%>.
